            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "美國政府宣布：撤銷「溫室氣體危害認定」",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"美國政府宣布：撤銷「溫室氣體危害認定」\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/QUmlQpz5iRUnTyNIC8ikKA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MA--/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2026-02/fe36e190-08ad-11f1-a835-605218538f1c\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">美國政府宣布：撤銷「溫室氣體危害認定」</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E5%AE%A3%E5%B8%83-%E6%92%A4%E9%8A%B7-%E6%BA%AB%E5%AE%A4%E6%B0%A3%E9%AB%94%E5%8D%B1%E5%AE%B3%E8%AA%8D%E5%AE%9A-055301826.html",
